title: 820-3462 No fan, orange light on magsafe without battery connected
message:
Orange light on Magsafe with and without battery.

title: 820-3462 No fan, orange light on magsafe without battery connected
message:
Q7100 is shorted and has already killed the CPU. RIP.

But if you want to try anyway replace U7100 AND Q7100.
